  STALKER-MP static library (Sprint-001).
  Integrates into Engine/xray-monolith/src/engine-vs2022.sln following the
  same configuration model as the engine's simple static libraries (the
  15 solution configurations map onto the 4 engine-facing configurations
  below: Release, Release-AVX, ProfiledDX11, Verified; Debug exists for the
  standalone Multiplayer/xrMP.sln only).
  Paths are anchored to this file so the project loads identically from the
  engine solution and from the module solution.
-->
